'''''Amma Pillai''''' is a [[1990 in film|1990]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]], [[Film director|directed]] by R. C. Shakthi and produced by M. K. Raju. It stars [[Ramki]] and [[Seetha (actress)|Seetha]] in the lead roles. It is a remake of the Malayalam film ''[[Mortuary (1983 Indian film)|Mortuary]]''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Amma Pillai Vinyl LP Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/42/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424014652/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F42%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

